Cậu làm gì thế hả?

201
00:16:17,943 --> 00:16:20,605
Ashley! Chó chết!

202
00:16:32,758 --> 00:16:36,250
Travis?

203
00:16:37,997 --> 00:16:39,430
Travis?

204
00:16:39,565 --> 00:16:41,533
Travis?

205
00:16:46,138 --> 00:16:49,539
Có cái gì dưới nước ấy!

206
00:16:49,675 --> 00:16:51,609
Cứu với!

207
00:16:51,744 --> 00:16:54,338
Có ai không!

208
00:16:55,647 --> 00:16:58,810
Ai cứu tôi với! Ashley!

209
00:17:05,224 --> 00:17:08,022
Travis. Thôi nào, cậu còn đó không?

210
00:17:08,160 --> 00:17:09,889
Travis?

211
00:17:10,029 --> 00:17:11,758
Travis!

212
00:17:13,499 --> 00:17:17,492
- Ashley!
